# ASCII hyphen only for breaks and ranges

Do not use Unicode EM DASH (U+2014) or EN DASH (U+2013), including between numbers in ranges or years.

Use a single ASCII hyphen-minus (U+002D, `-`) instead (e.g. `Weeks 1-4`, `2019-2024`, `Months 2-4`).

When editing inherited content that still uses U+2014 or U+2013, replace with `-`.
